Class QueueItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azwave.androidzwave.zwave.items.QueueItem

  • public class QueueItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Represent an Item of the PriorityBlockingQueue in the class QueueManager. Contains all this informations necessary to send a Msg.
